## Quick Start

```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd {{ project_name | lower | replace(' ', '-') }}
./keel install
```

## Development

```bash
./keel status             # Show stack configuration
./keel lint               # Run all linters
./keel test               # Run all tests
./keel format             # Auto-format code
./keel security-scan      # Run security scanners
./keel hooks run          # Run pre-commit hooks
./keel context refresh    # Update AI context files
{% if mempalace_enabled %}./keel memory status      # MemPalace status
./keel context live       # Sync MemPalace to context files
{% endif %}```

Filter by language:

```bash
./keel lint --lang python
./keel test --lang go
```

## Stack Configuration

Edit `keel.yml` to change your engineering stack, then regenerate:

```bash
./keel status             # What's configured now
./keel diff               # Preview changes
./keel regenerate         # Apply changes
```

